text: Patriarch John XI may refer to: * John XI Yeshu, Syriac Orthodox Patriarch of Antioch in 1208–1220 * John XI of Constantinople, Ecumenical Patriarch in 1275–1282 * Pope John XI of Alexandria, Pope of Alexandria & Patriarch of the See of St. Mark in 1427–1452 * John XI Helou, Maronite Patriarch of Antioch in 1809–1823
title: Patriarch John XI
